text: (upbeat music)

- Fannie Mae is a leading
source of mortgage financing.

We ensure that affordable
housing is accessible

to all home buyers and renters
throughout the country.
We have been going through
this digital transformation journey
with three major objectives.

The first one is drive the
operational efficiencies

such that we can actually
deliver more business capability
with existing capacity.

The second one is improve
the speed to the market
of our solutions to the marketplace,

so that our customers can
benefit from them very quickly.

And then the third one
is, improve our stability

and resiliency of the
platforms and the enterprise.
We have migrated hundreds of applications

and we have built some hundred
plus new application on AWS,
which has helped us in a significant way.

We have built certain accelerators,
technology accelerators,

where your first day one
application environment build
is happening in the first day itself.

What normally took about
three to four weeks.

We have seen almost
three X loan applications
coming through on a daily basis.

And we were able to scale our
applications pretty easily
because we had elasticity in place.
